# ⚔️ Ironhold Chess

> **Two armies. One board. No mercy.**

**Ironhold Chess** is a cinematic browser-based chess experience where traditional chess meets animated battlefield combat. Every piece is a unique warrior silhouette with custom SVG artwork, animated combat sequences, sound effects, visual themes, and an AI opponent.

🌐 **Live Demo:** [adithyanhp.github.io/Ironhold-Chess](https://adithyanhp.github.io/Ironhold-Chess/)

---

## 🎮 Features

### ♟️ Chess Gameplay
*   **Standard Rules**: Full validation for legal moves, check, checkmate, stalemate, and draws.
*   **Special Moves**: Complete support for castling, en passant, and pawn promotion.
*   **Match Tracking**: Move history, captured pieces, and real-time material advantage calculation.
*   **Flexibility**: Move undo and dynamic board flipping.

### ⚔️ Animated Battle System
*   **Combat Sequences**: Piece-specific attack animations and movement.
*   **Impact Physics**: Defender reactions, knockback, collapse effects, and impact flashes.
*   **Atmosphere**: Dynamic board shake effects and ambient smoke.

### 🛡️ Warrior Pieces
Each piece features custom SVG shapes and distinct CSS animations:

| Chess Piece | Warrior Design |
| :--- | :--- |
| ♙ Pawn | Foot Soldier |
| ♘ Knight | Mounted Warrior |
| ♗ Bishop | Hooded Mystic |
| ♖ Rook | Hulking Guardian |
| ♕ Queen | Regal Twin-Blade Warrior |
| ♔ King | Crowned Warlord |

### 🤖 Ironhold AI
Play against a built-in evaluation system weighing material, positioning, mobility, and safety.
*   **Recruit** — Easy
*   **Veteran** — Medium
*   **Warlord** — Hard

### 🎨 Customization & Audio
*   **Army Themes**: Molten Gold/Obsidian, Neon/Shadow, Ice/Fire, and Bone/Blood Moon.
*   **Procedural Audio**: Web Audio API movement sounds, capture impacts, and check notifications.
*   **UI/UX**: Full battle chronicle panel and responsive layouts for desktop, tablet, and mobile.

