## 🕹️ Getting Started

### Play Online
Visit the live deployment instantly: [Ironhold Chess Live](https://adithyanhp.github.io/Ironhold-Chess/)

### Run Locally
No installation or build process is required. 

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/adithyanhp/Ironhold-Chess.git
   ```
2. Navigate to the project directory:
   ```bash
   cd Ironhold-Chess
   ```
3. Open `index.html` in any modern web browser.

---

## 🧩 Controls

| Action | Control |
| :--- | :--- |
| Select / Move | Click piece, then click legal destination |
| Pawn Promotion | Selection overlay popup |
| Undo Move | `Undo Move` button |
| Rotate Board | `Flip Board` button |
| Settings | Toggle themes, audio, or start a `New Game` |

