---

## 🎯 Project Vision

Most browser chess games focus purely on the board. **Ironhold Chess focuses on the battle.** The goal is to create an experience where every move feels meaningful and every capture feels like a true clash of swords.

> **Chess is strategy. Ironhold Chess is strategy at war.**

